ai-tika-vin07t51:1_0: He should know about various colors, etc.,
ai-tika-vin07t51:2_1: The Saṅgha of the great disciples is said to wander in battle, who is falternative.
ai-tika-vin07t51:2_2: With clothes, thighs, and so on:
ai-tika-vin07t51:2_4: The person who is helpful should know whether or not they should be given to a community, who should be given to a community, and who should be given to a community.
ai-tika-vin07t51:3_0: The training rule on emission of semen is dropping, with blue makeup, and with blue makeup, and so on.
ai-tika-vin07t51:3_1: for this is said in the colour of blue, blue-coloured in colour and blue appearance.
ai-tika-vin07t51:3_2: Backly, you look here and now:
ai-tika-vin07t51:4_0: ‘Sometimes it is in the noble truth because they are undetermined in this way: “In those who speak in the noble ones, bad one is fit to be given to the Dhamma, no matter what is wrong.”
ai-tika-vin07t51:5_0: your commentary on the fortunate, etc., is finished.
